pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 17:01:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-153/0000018e-1ee4-d1cc-abfe-dfed18030000</guid></item><item><title>“要么以色列成为一个真正的共和国，要么成为一个十字军国家——圣经和剑”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/magazine/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/either-israel-becomes-a-true-republic-or-a-crusader-state-of-bible-and-sword/0000018e-1add-d8a6-a7de-3efd32a40000</link><description>科学史家阿夫纳·本扎肯认为，以色列所有问题的根源在于其选举制度。将其改为更直接、基于选区的系统可以改变我们的生活</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 16:56:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/magazine/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/either-israel-becomes-a-true-republic-or-a-crusader-state-of-bible-and-sword/0000018e-1add-d8a6-a7de-3efd32a40000</guid></item><item><title>印度档案：以色列与印度极右翼的友好关系早在莫迪之前几十年就开始了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-india-file-israels-warm-ties-with-the-indian-far-right-began-decades-before-modi/0000018e-19a9-d7d3-abce-79a999a10000</link><description>最近向公众公开的数千份以色列文件揭示了从 20 世纪 60 年代中期开始，以色列如何与印度的印度教民族主义政党建立关系 — — 尽管以色列外交官知道他们面对的是出于对穆斯林仇恨的极端分子</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 14:01:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-india-file-israels-warm-ties-with-the-indian-far-right-began-decades-before-modi/0000018e-19a9-d7d3-abce-79a999a10000</guid></item><item><title>拜登国情咨文：以色列在加沙浪费了美国的信贷额度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/bidens-state-of-the-union-israel-wasted-americas-credit-line-in-gaza/0000018e-1d98-d1cc-abfe-dfbd9e940000</link><description>美国开创了一个戏剧性的先例：以色列并不完全是加沙的发号施令者。如果以色列对抵抗外国势力在飞地的存在抱有幻想，那么临时港口的事实证明恰恰相反</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 13:47:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/bidens-state-of-the-union-israel-wasted-americas-credit-line-in-gaza/0000018e-1d98-d1cc-abfe-dfbd9e940000</guid></item><item><title>高等法院宣布部长解雇以色列邮政局主席的决定无效</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/high-court-of-justice-nullifies-ministers-dismissal-of-israel-postal-services-chairman/0000018e-1d26-dd0d-a98f-9d2e3c380000</link><description>法官们裁定，内阁部长卡希和阿姆萨勒姆的决定无效，并且可能不利于以色列邮政正在进行的私有化进程。一位法官称解雇“极其不合理”</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 11:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/high-court-of-justice-nullifies-ministers-dismissal-of-israel-postal-services-chairman/0000018e-1d26-dd0d-a98f-9d2e3c380000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学因学生反对而取消以巴冲突会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-college-cancels-conference-on-israel-palestine-conflict-after-students-object/0000018e-1d23-d1cc-abfe-dfaf9f410000</link><description>特拉维夫基布兹教育学院决定取消原计划举行的冲突历史教学会议，重点关注以色列和巴勒斯坦的叙述，此前一些学生和右翼活动人士认为该会议“敏感且具有攻击性”</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 09:05:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-college-cancels-conference-on-israel-palestine-conflict-after-students-object/0000018e-1d23-d1cc-abfe-dfaf9f410000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列准备应对国际社会对加沙的强烈反对，达成人质协议的可能性似乎很低</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/chances-for-a-hostage-deal-seem-low-as-israel-braces-for-international-backlash-over-gaza/0000018e-1a4c-d1cc-abfe-dfedb19b0000</link><description>时任国防部长埃胡德·巴拉克 (Ehud Barak) 曾于 2011 年警告以色列可能遭遇“外交海啸”。当这种情况没有发生时，他的警告遭到了内塔尼亚胡的忠实支持者的嘲笑。但考虑到加沙旷日持久的战争，这就是以色列现在面临的问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 04:00:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/chances-for-a-hostage-deal-seem-low-as-israel-braces-for-international-backlash-over-gaza/0000018e-1a4c-d1cc-abfe-dfedb19b0000<