18e-1a5b-d7d3-abce-7afbcd210000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡获得了从斯宾塞·帕特里奇那里贷款的许可，后者此前曾给他买过雪茄和西装。这笔贷款是由总理亲自挑选的国家审计长批准的，该审计长应该通过内塔尼亚胡的资产和利息披露来监督还款，而公众无法获得这些信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 22:39:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/only-one-man-knows-if-netanyahu-repaid-loan-from-millionaire-friend-and-hes-not-saying/0000018e-1a5b-d7d3-abce-7afbcd210000</guid></item><item><title>“这是一场残酷的富人之间的战争。以色列在加沙的战斗形式异常浪费”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/magazine/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-a-war-of-cruel-rich-people-israels-form-of-combat-in-gaza-is-unusually-wasteful/0000018e-1aa8-d1cc-abfe-dfadbc010000</link><description>加沙战争中出现的弹药相关问题将在稍后进行调查。与此同时，他们正在决定军队的战略，并使以色列完全依赖其美国盟友</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 21:35:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/magazine/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-a-war-of-cruel-rich-people-israels-form-of-combat-in-gaza-is-unusually-wasteful/0000018e-1aa8-d1cc-abfe-dfadbc010000</guid></item><item><title>正统派政党达成解决拜特谢梅什市长选举决选的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/haredi-parties-cut-deal-to-resolve-run-off-in-beit-shemesh-mayoral-election/0000018e-1a83-d7d3-abce-7aab6cad0000</link><description>Degel Hatorah、Agudat Yisrael 和 Shas 之间的合作协议预计也将对 Bnei Brak 的市政政治和下一次议会选举产生影响</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 20:49:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/haredi-parties-cut-deal-to-resolve-run-off-in-beit-shemesh-mayoral-election/0000018e-1a83-d7d3-abce-7aab6cad0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙迫切需要援助。拜登找到解决办法了吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-07/ty-article/.highlight/gaza-desperately-needs-aid-is-bidens-new-emergency-port-plan-the-answer/0000018e-19ed-dec4-abcf-dfefa9150000</link><description>由于未能确保停火，紧急港口将成为拜登在国情咨文演讲期间发表的以色列-加沙言论的核心内容。随着斋月的临近，每一分钟的风险都呈指数级增长</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 20:42:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-07/ty-article/.highlight/gaza-desperately-needs-aid-is-bidens-new-emergency-port-plan-the-answer/0000018e-19ed-dec4-abcf-dfefa9150000</guid></item><item><title>以色列获准参加下个月的欧洲歌唱大赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-given-permission-to-participate-in-next-months-eurovision-contest/0000018e-1a3d-d8fb-abff-5f3f935c0000</link><description>经过数周的不确定性和对以色列必须待在家里的真正担忧之后，欧洲广播联盟批准了《飓风》的歌词，该歌词将于周日在 Kan 11 的特别广播中首播</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 19:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-given-permission-to-participate-in-next-months-eurovision-contest/0000018e-1a3d-d8fb-abff-5f3f935c0000</guid></item><item><title>今年妇女节，加沙的巴勒斯坦妇女正在帐篷里制作经期产品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-womens-day-palestinian-women-in-gaza-are-making-period-products-out-of-tents/0000018e-1980-d7d3-abce-79a9bfa90000</link><description>加沙妇女在面临水危机时剪掉头发、在没有麻醉的情况下剖腹产并用废料制作经期产品，在不可能的情况下展现了力量和聪明才智</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 19:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-womens-day-palestinian-women-in-gaza-are-making-period-products-out-of-tents/0000018e-1980-d7d3-abce-79a9bfa90000</guid></item><item><title>OSINT 揭示了自 10 月 7 日以来美国向以色列空运武器的规模空前</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/open-source-intelligence-reveals-the-unprecedented-extent-of-u-s-arms-airlifts-to-israel/0000018e-1976-d021-adef-9f77c76c0000</link><description>据报道，自加沙战争爆发以来，拜登政府已向以色列秘密出售了 100 笔武器。公开的飞行数据显示了它是如何展开的</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 18:35:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/open-source-intelligence-reveals-the-unprecedented-extent-of-u-s-arms-airlifts-to-israel/0000018e-1976-d021-adef-9f77c76c0000</guid></item><item><title>战时的斋月和阿克萨清真寺：加沙战争将如何影响以色列和巴勒斯坦的关键热点？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article-timeline/.premium/ramadan-and-al-aqsa-in-wartime-the-gaza-war-and-a-key-israeli-palestinian-flashpoint/0000018e-0ef9-d203-a9ce-1ef989420000</link><description>随着斋月下周开始，本已动荡的中东将面临另一场考验，重点是耶路撒冷的阿克萨清真寺。加沙战争将如何影响以色列和巴勒斯坦的关键热点？ |国土报解释</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 18:15:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article-timeline/.premium/ramadan-and-al-aqsa-in-wartime-the-gaza-war-and-a-key-israeli-palestinian-flashpoint/0000018e-0ef9-d203-a9ce-1ef989420000</guid></item></channel></rss>